## Limitations

The data presented in this report is subject to limitations inherent in survey methodologies, such as sample size and demographic representation. Additionally, public opinion on abortion can be influenced by recent political events and media coverage, which may not be fully captured in the available data. Furthermore, the complexity of individual beliefs about abortion may not be entirely reflected in binary pro-choice or pro-life categorizations.